Online forex trading company 51 Capital on Thursday presented its innovative commitment to their CSR, titled 'One Child Coin'. The initiative seeks to engage the millions of children aged 10-18 idling at home in an online essay writing competition. It will award the most fluent and gifted children with a scholarship, a fully funded cryptocurrency account (pessacoin) or a placement in one of the leading virtual money companies in town. The campaign will elevate in due time.